node.text:
TUDOR announces a major new partnership with @alaia.bay / @alaia.chalet - a visionary concept revolving around action sports. Alaia Bay, is the first wave pool in continental Europe. +8.500 m² to surf, all skill levels. New surf spot for a perfect swell in the heart of the Swiss Alps.

#TudorWatch #BornToDare

node.title: TUDOR : A major new partnership with Alaïa

node.text:
Discover the TUDOR Black Bay Ceramic, an extraordinary watch and symbol of the brand’s technical expertise, with a case in matt black ceramic, a Manufacture Calibre and a #MasterChronometer certification from METAS.

Find out more by clicking on the product tag or the link in bio.

#TudorWatch#BorntoDare #BlackBayCeramic #MasterChronometer

node.title: Introducing the new TUDOR Black Bay Ceramic watch 2021

node.text: It was one year ago, Morgan Bourc’his won his second world championship title. Greatest champions aren’t just athletes. There is always something more behind, just as there is something more in a #TudorWatch. @morganbourchis says it, not us. Stay Tuned for new adventures - November 17th.
